summary: Devianart Hates me so much so I had to do this in MS Pain(t). DX Finished up a drawing of Retsuko in the animal crossing style...
caption:
Devianart Hates me so much so I had to do this in MS Pain(t). DX

Finished up a drawing of Retsuko in the animal crossing style that I did. This was a bit hard as they do not have red pandas in the game. I have the original sketch on the Aggretsuko amino. I will do the others one day

Also did you know they actually did Sanrio item sets that you could get via amiibo cards?
I managed to get the Hello kitty set from someone.

(Also no pants. Woo)

Retsuko belongs to Snario
Animal crossing belongs to Nintendo
I couldn’t find the original background. I got it from Pintrest so if anyone knows where the original background is from then let me know please
